China [ Summary ] Sixty - eight patients with type 2 diabetes were divided into 2 groups . The patients in two groups were given metformin or pioglitazone / metformin treatment respectively for 12 weeks . The level of serum interleukin - 6 ( IL - 6 ) ,	O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O B-Anatomy E-Anatomy O O O
vaspin ,	O O
adiponectin ,	O O
blood glucose ,	O O O
and other indicators before and after the treatment in patients of two groups were observed . After the treatment ,	O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O
the level of serum IL - 6 and adiponectin changed significantly in pioglitazone / metformin group ( P < 0 . 05 ,	O O O O B-Anatomy E-Anatomy O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O
P < 0 . 01 ) . The 2hPG and HBA1C in metformin group were higher than that in pioglitazone / metformin group ( P < 0 . 01 ,	O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O
P < 0 . 05 ) . The rate of BMI change was not related with the rate of adipocytokines change ,	O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O
so was the rate of HBA1C change . Effects of pioglitazone / metformin on blood glucose and adipocytokines were more significant than metformin alone ,	O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O
which did not depend on the decrease of glucose level and body weight . [ Key words ] Diabetes mellitus ,	O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O
