China [ Abstract ] Objective To investigate the role of aquaglyceroporin 7 ( AQP7 ) played in insulin resistance of adipocytes . Methods 3T3 - L1 preadipocyte cells were induced to be fully differentiated adipocytes and then insulin resistance was induced by dexamethasone ( DXM ) . Adenovirus vector over - expressing AQP7 ( Ad - AQP7 ) was constructed and transfected into adipocytes . Expression levels of AQP7 ,	O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O
glycerol release from adipocytes ,	O O O O O
changes in glucose consumption ,	O O O O O
and phosphorylated protein kinase B ( p - PKB ) were measured . Results 48 h - treatment of dexamethasone significantly inhibited the expression level of p - PKB ( P < 0 . 01 ) and decreased glucose utilization ,	O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O
as well as down - regulation of AQP7 ( P < 0 . 01 ) . Over - expression of AQP7 by transfecting Ad - AQP7 to dexamethasone ( DXM ) - induced insulin resistant adipocytes could improve glycerol secretion of adipocytes ,	O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O
being consistent with the restoration of p - PKB expression levels and glucose consumption . Conclusions AQP7 may improve in molecular mechanism of insulin resistance in adipocytes . Overexpression of AQP7 may contribute to the improvement of insulin resistance in adipocytes and might be correlated with better phosphorylation of PKB . [ Key words ] Aquaglyceroporin 7 ;	O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O
